Following the outbreak of the {{ill|Ōnin War|ja|応仁の乱|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the emperor and retired emperor evacuated to {{ill|Muromachi Palace|ja|室町殿|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, while the Imperial Palace was occupied by {{ill|Toki Shigeyori|ja|土岐成頼|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and the Sento Imperial Palace by {{ill|Hatakeyama Yoshinari|ja|畠山義就|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, leading to the suspension of all court ceremonies.{{Sfn|Makoto Nakamoto|2021|p=34}} 

